This is my personal attempt to learn Python.
So far the scripts support grayscale images only. 
If you provide a RGB image it will be converted to grayscale

Try some of the SIPI images like the following:
http://sipi.usc.edu/database/download.php?vol=misc&img=5.1.09
http://sipi.usc.edu/database/download.php?vol=misc&img=5.2.08